00:20.277 --> 00:23.999
The RPAC conference is gonna
honor you, Mr. President.

00:24.000 --> 00:25.999
- What do you mean "family"?
- I'm pregnant.

00:26.000 --> 00:28.999
- Chuy, I'm out.
- Yeah?

00:29.000 --> 00:30.999
The best fucking agent that ever lived

00:31.000 --> 00:31.999
got you your own show.

00:32.000 --> 00:33.999
My mom always loved you, sir.

00:34.000 --> 00:35.999
She worked the Graves
For President office

