00:49.000 --> 00:50.999
Then I graduated summa cum laude,

00:51.000 --> 00:51.999
president of Hasty Pudding.

00:52.000 --> 00:53.999
Of course, you might have read that.

00:54.000 --> 00:56.530
The three and a half years
I spent at Harvard...

00:56.531 --> 00:57.999
