Hey, this is Erin York with "USA Today."

28:55.823 --> 28:59.822
We met a little while ago at that
Chamber of Commerce reception in DC.

28:59.823 --> 29:01.822
Oh, yeah, yeah, yeah.
I remember. Hi, Erin.

